      "para_id": "Q005031.1",
      "line_range": "1",
      "translation": "(1) To Nergal of Aldak , his master , Warad-Erra , gudug priest of Nergal , son of Adalal , the gudug priest , his servant , dedicated this ( mace ) for the well-being of Išme-Dagan , the powerful king , king of Isin , king of Sumer and Akkad ."
    }
  ],
